Module com.example.bankingtransactionsgui
Package com.example.bank

Class CollegeChecking

java.lang.Object
com.example.bank.Account
com.example.bank.Checking
com.example.bank.CollegeChecking
public class CollegeChecking
extends Checking
The type of account is a College Checking account. Different variables define the characteristics of the class such as interest rate and monthly fees. Implement different methods to calculate interest and fees of the account.
Author:
Akshat Mehta and Atharva Patil
